      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SHOT OF MAGIC (3) is progressing well and looks close to another win after hitting the frame last run (20.22) at Grafton. Has a strong winning record at this journey. Good beginner aided by a nice draw. Winning claims. FEDERAL FELIX (1) returned a better run last time, finishing in the money (22.95) at this track behind Drink Twisties in a Grade 5. Stalked the pace but found the line strongly. Safe beginner who draws ideally on the inside. Expecting another good run. JAKEY BLUE (6) hit the frame latest (24.89) when third at Gunnedah in a Grade 4/5. Has already won two times from this draw. Looks suited here and can measure up. ICEBERG AHEAD (8) was below best last time at Grafton (20.70) in a Grade 5, finishing a 9 length seventh. Already a winner from this draw.",
